=== QUICK START ===

You must have bowtie2 installed on your
system for breseq to function!

Run this command to get breseq help
$ bin/breseq

You may run this command to test the breseq install:
$ ./run_tests.sh

If you relocate the files in the 'bin' directory, then you
must also relocate the files in the 'share' directory to the
same location relative to the binaries (../share/breseq).

=== FOR MORE INFORMATION ===

